3a:["$","p",null,{"children":["唔會。Skills 同 Tools 係分開管理嘅。裝 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"obsidian"}]," Skill 唔會自動開 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"write"}]," Tool。呢個係安全設計——你需要明確決定畀哪些權限 Agent，唔係裝個 Skill 就自動獲得所有所需權限。如果 Skill 需要某個 Tool 但你冇開，Agent 會話佢你需要先開對應權限。"]}]
3b:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：可唔可以自己寫 Skill？"}]}]
3c:["$","p",null,{"children":["可以。Skill 本質上係一個 Markdown 格式嘅教學文件，教 Agent 點樣用某個工具或服務。你可以寫自己公司嘅內部工具 Skill、自己嘅工作流程 Skill，甚至上載去 ClawHub 分享。自己寫嘅 Skill 只存係本地，唔需要安裝，直接放喺 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"~/.openclaw/skills/"}]," 目錄即可。"]}]
3d:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：裝咗幾多 Skills 先算「太多」？"}]}]
3e:["$","p",null,{"children":"質比量重要。我建議裝少少但用緊嘅，唔好見到有趣就裝。每個 Skill 都可能帶嚟安全風險（尤其是社區 Skill），而且太多 Skill 會增加 context window 佔用，影響 Agent 判斷。我自己只裝我實際每星期都用到嘅 Skills，目前係 8 個左右。"}]
3f:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：ClawHub 上邊啲 Skill 千祈唔好裝？"}]}]
40:["$","ul",null,{"className":"my-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 marker:text-red-600","children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"冇 Security Scan 結果嘅社區 Skill（尤其係下載量高但冇評論）"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"要求跟功能唔相符嘅過份權限嘅 Skill"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"源碼係 obfuscated（混淆過）嘅 Skill"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"只有一個 Skill 嘅新帳號作者發布嘅 Skill"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":["要求讀取 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"~/.ssh"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"~/.aws"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"~/Library/Keychains"}]," 等敏感目錄嘅 Skill"]}],"\n"]}]
41:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：點樣移除已裝嘅 Skill？"}]}]
